koheriki
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:[Ma.] a highly perfumed native plant, smelling of aniseed and added by shepherds to tobacco.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
